            <header>
                <h1 class="entry-title">I served in Afghanistan as a US Marine, twice. Here’s the truth in two sentences</h1>

                

                <div class="meta-info">

                    <div class="td-post-author-name"><div class="td-author-by">By</div> <a href="https://usmclife.com/author/mike/">Staff Writer</a><div class="td-author-line"> - </div> </div>                    <span class="td-post-date"><time class="entry-date updated td-module-date" datetime="2021-08-23T12:51:48+00:00" >August 23, 2021</time></span>                    <div class="td-post-views"><i class="td-icon-views"></i><span class="td-nr-views-52476">907</span></div>                    <div class="td-post-comments"><a href="https://usmclife.com/i-served-in-afghanistan-as-a-us-marine-twice-heres-the-truth-in-two-sentences/#respond"><i class="td-icon-comments"></i>0</a></div>                </div>
            </header>


        </div>

        <div class="td-post-sharing td-post-sharing-top td-pb-padding-side"><span class="td-post-share-title">SHARE</span>
