	                <a class="td-social-sharing-buttons td-social-whatsapp" href="whatsapp://send?text=I+served+in+Afghanistan+as+a+US+Marine%2C+twice.+Here%E2%80%99s+the+truth+in+two+sentences%20-%20https%3A%2F%2Fusmclife.com%2Fi-served-in-afghanistan-as-a-us-marine-twice-heres-the-truth-in-two-sentences%2F" ><div class="td-sp td-sp-whatsapp"></div></a>
